    {
      "description": "Start by doing a small real job in Google Cloud: create a project, open Cloud Shell, put a file in Cloud Storage, and run a simple service. The goal is to touch the console, IAM prompts, billing, and logs right away without needing prior cloud experience.",
      "title": "Your First Working Service in Google Cloud"
    },
