    },
    {
      "description": "Identity decides who can do what, and mistakes here cause real damage fast. You’ll work with users, service accounts, roles, policies, and least-privilege patterns that teams use every day.",
      "title": "IAM and Service Accounts"
    },
    {
      "description": "Networks are the roads your systems use. This chapter covers VPCs, subnets, firewall rules, routes, load balancers, DNS, private access, and the practical choices behind secure connectivity.",
      "title": "VPC Networks and Traffic Flow"
    },
