      "title": "Kubernetes with GKE"
    },
    {
      "description": "Applications need durable storage in different forms. This chapter covers Cloud Storage, Persistent Disk, Filestore, storage classes, lifecycle rules, and how to choose the right storage for each job.",
      "title": "Storage Options in Practice"
